@startuml ZMQ RPC Metrics — Current Code (2026-05 sync)
' Companion to timing_points.puml: 叙事版见旧图；本图对齐 yuanrong-datasystem 当前实现。
' 编号 [1]–[7] = 墙体时刻 tick；[8][9] = RecordServerLatencyMetrics 写入的合成刻度（时长字段，非同源时钟）。
!pragma teoz true
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam actorBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBorderColor #666666
skinparam lifelineBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

title **ZMQ RPC ticks & histograms — lifecycle** (numbered <color:#C62828>wall</color> + <color:#AD1457>synthetic</color>)

participant "Caller" as C <<Client>>
box "Client side" #LightBlue
participant "AsyncWriteImpl\n(zmq_stub_impl.h)" as AW
participant "SendAll /\nSendConnMsg\n(unary,\nzmq_unary_client_impl.h)" as UN
participant "AsyncReadImpl /\nReadImpl" as AR
end box
participant "MsgQueRef /\noutbound" as R <<Queue>>
participant "MsgQueMgr prefetch\n→ Outbound()" as OB <<Route>>
participant "ZmqFrontend::SendMsg\n(zmq_stub_conn.cpp)" as FE <<Frontend>>
participant "Frontend msgQue_\n(+ async send thread)" as AS <<AsyncGW>>
database "TCP / IPC" as Net
participant "ZmqService /\nFrontendToBackend …" as SRV <<Server>>
participant "WorkerEntry\n(zmq_service.cpp)" as W <<Worker>>
participant "Unary Write() /\nSendAll()\n(zmq_server_stream_base.h)" as UW <<Reply>>
participant "ZmqService::\nServiceToClient /\nroutingFn_ reply Put" as STC <<Backend>>
participant "ZmqServerImpl::\nServiceToClient" as IMPL <<GW>>

note top
<b>Legend — MetaPb.tick_name</b> (<b>zmq_constants.h</b>)

<color:#C62828><b>[1] CLIENT_ENQUEUE</b></color> — <b>zmq_stub_impl.h</b> <b>AsyncWriteImpl</b> before <b>mQue->SendMsg</b>; unary <b>SendAll</b> 同步 (<b>zmq_unary_client_impl.h</b>).

<color:#C62828><b>[2] CLIENT_TO_STUB</b></color> — <b>zmq_stub_conn.cpp</b> <b>Outbound</b> 首行（prefetch 出队后，仍在前端 inner queue / <b>zmq_msg_send</b> 之前）. Unary <b>SendConnMsg</b> 可补打若缺。

(无 <b>MetaPb</b> tick 于真正 <b>zmq_msg_send</b> 完成处) — <b>CLIENT_ZMQ_SEND</b> 仍缺。

<color:#C62828><b>[7] CLIENT_RECV</b></color> — <b>AsyncReadImpl</b> / unary <b>ReadImpl</b> 收包后；<b>RecordRpcLatencyMetrics</b>。Async 路径合并 <b>clientMeta.ticks</b>（<b>MetaHasNamedTick</b> 去重）。

<color:#C62828><b>[3] SERVER_RECV</b></color> — <b>ZmqService::FrontendToBackend</b>。

<color:#C62828><b>[4] SERVER_DEQUEUE</b></color> / <color:#C62828><b>[5] SERVER_EXEC_END</b></color> — <b>WorkerEntry</b>：<b>ReceiveMsg</b> 后 / <b>WorkerEntryImpl</b> 结束后。Unary <b>Write</b>/<b>SendAll</b> 可更早打 <b>[5]</b>，避免 <b>(SEND − 0)</b>。

<color:#C62828><b>[6] SERVER_SEND</b></color> — <b>ServiceToClient</b>；或 <b>!multiDestinations_</b> 时 <b>routingFn_</b> 在 <b>replyQueue_->Put</b> 前同样打 <b>[6]</b> + <b>RecordServerLatencyMetrics</b>。

<color:#AD1457><b>[8] SERVER_EXEC_NS</b></color> / <color:#AD1457><b>[9] SERVER_RPC_WINDOW_NS</b></color> — 合成：由 <b>RecordServerLatencyMetrics</b> 追加（<b>[5]−[3]</b> 与 <b>[6]−[3]</b> 等）。

<b>Histograms</b>（<b>KvMetricId → kv_metrics.cpp 导出名</b>，µs：<b>NsToUs</b>）

* <b>zmq_client_queuing_latency</b> ← <color:#C62828><b>[2]−[1]</b></color>
* <b>zmq_server_queue_wait_latency</b> ← <color:#C62828><b>[4]−[3]</b></color>
* <b>zmq_server_exec_latency</b> ← <color:#C62828><b>[5]−[4]</b></color>
* <b>zmq_server_reply_latency</b> ← <color:#C62828><b>[6]−[5]</b></color>（仅当 <b>[5]</b> wall > 0）
* <b>zmq_rpc_e2e_latency</b> ← <color:#C62828><b>[7]−[1]</b></color>
* <b>zmq_rpc_network_latency</b> ← <b>残差</b>：<code>max(0, ([7]−[1])−([2]−[1])−srvWin)</code>，<code>srvWin</code>=<color:#AD1457><b>[9]</b></color>.ts <b>或</b> 回退 <color:#C62828><b>[6]−[3]</b></color>；仅 &gt;0 记入

end note

== Request (client, stub queue path) ==

C -> AW : AsyncWriteImpl
activate AW
AW -> AW : RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[1] CLIENT_ENQUEUE</b></color>
AW -> R : mQue->SendMsg(meta, frames)
activate R
R -> R : MsgQue outbound **enqueue**
R -> OB : prefetcher **PrefetchMsg** → **Outbound(...)**
activate OB
OB -> OB : RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[2] CLIENT_TO_STUB</b></color>
OB -> FE : **SendMsg**(→ inner queue / async gateway)
activate FE
FE -> AS : msgQue_->Send(…); later **RouteToZmqSocket** → **zmq_msg_send**
deactivate FE
deactivate OB
deactivate R
note over AS
  **无 MetaPb tick** 于 **zmq_msg_send** 完成处
end note
deactivate AW

== Request (unary non–exclusive, queue to frontend) ==

C -> UN : **SendAll** → **SendConnMsg** → **mQue_->SendMsg**
activate UN
UN -> UN : RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[1] CLIENT_ENQUEUE</b></color>
UN -> OB : same **Outbound** → <color:#C62828><b>[2]</b></color> on queued copy
UN -> UN : if meta lacks tick: RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[2] CLIENT_TO_STUB</b></color>
deactivate UN

AS -> Net : request bytes
Net -> SRV : delivery
activate SRV
SRV -> SRV : RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[3] SERVER_RECV</b></color>
SRV -> W : dispatch → **WorkerEntry**
activate W
W -> W : **ReceiveMsg** → RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[4] SERVER_DEQUEUE</b></color>
W -> UW : **CallMethod** → … **Write** / **SendAll**
activate UW
UW -> UW : optional early\n<color:#C62828><b>[5] SERVER_EXEC_END</b></color> (guarded)\n<b>enableMsgQ_</b>: <color:#C62828><b>[6]</b></color> in **ServiceToClient**, not in **Write**
UW -> STC : **mQue_->SendMsg** / reply path
deactivate UW

STC -> STC : **ServiceToClient** / **routingFn_**:\nRecordTick <color:#C62828><b>[6] SERVER_SEND</b></color>\n<b>RecordServerLatencyMetrics</b> → <color:#AD1457><b>[8][9]</b></color>
STC -> IMPL : replyQueue → **ServiceToClient** (when needed)
activate IMPL
IMPL -> IMPL : **SendAllFrames** (仍 **无** 独立 **TICK_SERVER_ZMQ_SEND**)
IMPL -> Net : response bytes
deactivate IMPL
deactivate W
deactivate SRV

Net -> AR : reply
activate AR
C -> AR : **AsyncReadImpl** / unary **ReadImpl**
AR -> AR : merge client ticks → RecordTick\n<color:#C62828><b>[7] CLIENT_RECV</b></color>
AR -> AR : **RecordRpcLatencyMetrics**

deactivate AR

== Notes for PR / docs ==
note across
  **相对 timing_points.puml**
  • 无字面 **CLIENT_DEQUEUE**；<color:#C62828><b>[2]</b></color> = prefetch 出队后 **Outbound** 首行。
  • Unary 与 Async 在 <color:#C62828><b>[1][2][7]</b></color> + **RecordRpcLatencyMetrics** 对齐；Unary 依赖 **SendConnMsg** 补 <color:#C62828><b>[2]</b></color>。
  • <b>!multiDestinations_</b> 时 **routingFn_** **Put** 前打 <color:#C62828><b>[6]</b></color>。
  • **PerfPoint**：**ZMQ_NETWORK_TRANSFER** 与 **ZMQ_RPC_NETWORK_LATENCY** 不同。
end note

@enduml
